Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and language models.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes an automatic approach for terminology enrichment.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses graph convolutional networks for embedding and alignment.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with measuring relevancy between terminologies and entities.
- cs.DB (Databases) is relevant as the paper deals with enriching medical terminology knowledge bases.
